@startuml
title Blog - Public List/View/Search
actor User
boundary WebApp
control Backend
collections Cache
database DB

User -> WebApp: Xem danh sách/tìm kiếm
WebApp -> Backend: GET /api/blog/posts?q=...
Backend -> Cache: Tra cache
alt Hit
  Cache --> Backend: Posts
  Backend --> WebApp: 200 {posts}
else Miss
  Backend -> DB: Query posts + enrich
  DB --> Backend: Posts
  Backend -> Cache: Set cache
  Backend --> WebApp: 200 {posts}
end
User -> WebApp: Xem chi tiết bài
WebApp -> Backend: GET /api/blog/posts/{slug}
Backend -> DB: Lấy bài + bình luận
DB --> Backend: Post + comments
Backend --> WebApp: 200 {post}
WebApp --> User: Hiển thị nội dung
@enduml

